This set of maps made by '''Bryant 'Gunrock' Robinson''' features seven maps in a dark brown environment. Taking place in an overtaken arctic base, Dark 7 ''forces'' you to complete a series of 'mission objectives', coded by scripts, guiding you and giving you the needed informations about your objective, what is happening, and what is expected from you.

It also has an [[Dark 7 Mission Pack|addon]].
